MLJ 0.2
-------

This directory contains the distribution for MLJ 0.2. In particular:

INSTALL    	contains minimum instructions for installation.
COPYING    	is the Gnu Public License under which MLJ 0.2 is distributed
index.html 	is the root of the HTML documentation.

doc/		contains documentation, in particular:
  mlj.dvi,mlj.ps        contain the MLJ User Guide.
  mljext.dvi,mljext.ps  document the MLJ Language Extensions.

src/		contains the source for the compiler and Basis Library
demos/		contains a number of demonstration programs
bin/		contains the MLJ binaries, when built



